<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yào qín láo zuò zhǔ gōng 迦南133</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yào qín láo zuò zhǔ gōng, fèng chà hé fāng yào fèn yǒng,
 yī shēng wú suǒ qiú, pāo qì lì lù gōng míng,
 lì zhì zài yé sū lǐ zuò yī míng jīng bīng,
 yǎn kàn tiān xià yún yún zhòng shēng,
 zài shuǐ shēn huǒ rè zuì è zhī zhōng,
 wǒ yuàn wǎng pǔ tiān xià qù chuán fú yīn,
 chuán fú yīn gěi wàn mín tīng.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>133</hymn_number>
</song>